data.description:
Look no further! This expansive 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home provides ample space, featuring an eat-in kitchen and a versatile formal dining area or office space. Enjoy the elegance of tile flooring throughout the main areas. With over 2,000 square feet of living space, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Don't overlook the covered patio and beautifully shaded backyard. Your ideal rental home awaits!

Tenant responsible for utilities and maintaining the lawn. Smoking prohibited. Small pets allowed, limited to 20 pounds.
